<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw sepgim leh buoina khelah,
 Chawlte di'n In nuomtak a um;
 Kithenna um ngeiloh na In,
 Kuo a chawl nuomlo ding ziechun?

[V2]
 Aw ngak hamin, phunchiek lohiel in!
 Aw ngak hamin, phunchiek lohiel in;
 Aw ngak hamin, ngakham in, phun loin!

[V3]
 2. Na puokgik in chau mahleh chin,
 Khawvel thilin hun delh mahleh;
 Dakin! chawlhna nuom tung inla,
 Ngak hamin, phunchiek dah maiin.

[V4]
 3. Na lampi-ah ling um mahleh,
 Aw Lalpa lu chuh ngaihtuoh in;
 Na lunggil hih-lungkham mahleh,
 Mi thiengtho zaw bawn a sun tai.

[V5]
 4. Gim mahleh chinle sem zelin,
 Paucham bangmah hengilh loin;
 Na chawlh nang ni anai ta ie,
 Ngak hamin, phunchiek lohiel in!</lyrics>
<title>WAIT, AND MURMUR NOT!</title>
<hymn_number>292</hymn_number>
</song>